<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <title>DomaHub - Domain Name Rentals</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/min/main_index.min.css" />
  <meta name="description" content="DomaHub provides domain name rentals at low, affordable prices and flexible time slots. Rent one today!" />
  <%- include("../templates/head_links"); %>
</head>

<body>

  <%- include("../templates/navbar", {user: user}); %>
  <section id="index-img" class="section is-large landing-img">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column is-6-desktop is-offset-3-desktop is-8-tablet is-offset-2-tablet">
          <div class="content">
            <h1 class="title is-1 is-white margin-bottom-25">
                The <span class="\">Hub</span> for renting <span class="">Doma</span>in names.
            </h1>
            <h2 class="subtitle is-5 is-white margin-bottom-25">
              DomaHub provides domain name rentals at low, affordable prices and flexible time slots.
            </h2>
          </div>
          <div class="content">
            <form class="beta-form">
              <div class="control is-grouped">
                <p class="control is-expanded">
                  <input tabindex="1" class="input is-expanded is-medium" type="email" name="betaemail" placeholder="Enter your email"/>
                </p>
                <p class="control">
                  <a tabindex="1" class="beta-submit button is-primary is-medium">Sign Up for Beta</a>
                </p>
              </div>
            </form>
            <div class="beta-form-success is-hidden">
              <div class="notification has-text-centered is-white">
                <h3 class="is-primary is-bold">Success! You have been put on the waiting list.</h3>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section is-medium">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column margin-bottom-75">
          <div class="content">
            <p class="is-grey is-bold heading">
              DOMAIN OWNERS
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="content">
            <h1 class="title is-2 has-text-centered has-style-underline">Don't let your domains rot away.</h1>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column is-5">
          <div class="content">
            <h2>Create a listing and start generating revenue!</h2>
            <p>
              List your domains on DomaHub and allow other users to rent it out.
              This way your unused domains don't just sit there - they help someone
              out while putting money in your pocket!
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="content margin-top-25">
            <h2 class="margin-bottom-15">Two types of listings</h2>
            <div class="columns">
              <div class="column">
                <div class="content">
                  <h3 class="is-bold is-accent tag is-medium">Basic</h3>
                  <p>
                    Free to list with a
                    15% commission on all successful rentals.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="column">
                <div class="content">
                  <h3 class="is-bold is-primary tag is-medium">Premium</h3>
                  <p>
                    $5 / month per listing with no commission
                    on your sales. You keep everything you earn.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <a tabindex="1" href="/sellers#basicvpremium" class="is-accent">
              Learn more about Basic and Premium Listings
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column is-6 is-offset-1">
          <div class="content margin-bottom-15">
            <h2>DomaHub Benefits</h2>
            <p>
              Click on each slider below to learn more.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="slider-box">
            <div class="slider-item" tabindex="1">
              <div class="slider-content">
                <span class="icon is-primary">
                  <i class="fa fa-id-card-o"></i>
                </span>
                <span>No ownership transfer</span>
              </div>
              <div class="slider-icon">
                <span class="icon is-primary">
                  <i class="fa fa-angle-down"></i>
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="slider-item-dropdown">
              <div class="content">
                <p>
                  You don't have to deal with the hassle of transferring ownership to
                  domain renters. We make renting simple by having renters redirect
                  web content to your domain. This way, there is no ownership transfer
                  and the whole process is quick and efficient.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="slider-item" tabindex="1">
              <div class="slider-content">
                <span class="icon is-primary">
                  <i class="fa fa-gears"></i>
                </span>
                <span>Custom pricing options</span>
              </div>
              <div class="slider-icon">
                <span class="icon is-primary">
                  <i class="fa fa-angle-down"></i>
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="slider-item-dropdown">
              <div class="content">
                <p>
                  Premium Listings have variable pricing. You decide how much
                  to rent out your domains for. On the other hand, Basic Listings
                  have fixed, default pricing. For more information on listing
                  pricing, please <a href="/sellers#basicvpremium" class="is-accent">click here.</a>
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="slider-item" tabindex="1">
              <div class="slider-content">
                <span class="icon is-primary">
                  <i class="fa fa-calendar-check-o"></i>
                </span>
                <span>Flexible rental scheduling</span>
              </div>
              <div class="slider-icon">
                <span class="icon is-primary">
                  <i class="fa fa-angle-down"></i>
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="slider-item-dropdown">
              <div class="content">
                <p>
                  Listings can be rented by the hour, day, week, or month. Basic
                  Listings are limited to weekly or monthly rentals whereas Premium
                  Listings can be rented for any of the four time rates.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="slider-item" tabindex="1">
              <div class="slider-content">
                <span class="icon is-primary">
                  <i class="fa fa-credit-card"></i>
                </span>
                <span>Quick, secure payments</span>
              </div>
              <div class="slider-icon">
                <span class="icon is-primary">
                  <i class="fa fa-angle-down"></i>
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="slider-item-dropdown">
              <div class="content">
                <p>
                  We use a payments processor called Stripe.
                  Stripe allows you to get paid quickly and securely.
                  For more information on payments visit <a href="https://www.stripe.com" class="is-accent">Stripe's website</a>
                  or read our <a href="/faq#payments" class="is-accent">FAQ.</a>
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section is-medium">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column margin-bottom-75">
          <div class="content">
            <p class="is-grey is-bold heading">
              DOMAIN RENTERS
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="content">
            <h1 class="title is-2 has-text-centered has-style-underline">Domain rentals work for you.</h1>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column is-5">
          <div class="content">
            <h2>Why rent a domain?</h2>
            <p>
              Domain rentals are cost-effective and always fit your schedule.
              Rent one today and see what you can create!
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column is-5 is-offset-1">
          <div class="columns">
            <div class="column is-half">
              <div class="checklist-item">
                <span class="icon is-accent">
                  <i class="fa fa-check"></i>
                </span>
                <span>Cost-effective Pricing</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="column is-half">
              <div class="checklist-item">
                <span class="icon is-accent">
                  <i class="fa fa-check"></i>
                </span>
                <span>Flexible Scheduling</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="columns">
            <div class="column is-half">
              <div class="checklist-item">
                <span class="icon is-accent">
                  <i class="fa fa-check"></i>
                </span>
                <span>Low Commitment</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="column is-half">
              <div class="checklist-item">
                <span class="icon is-accent">
                  <i class="fa fa-check"></i>
                </span>
                <span>Quick Turnaround</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column is-5">
          <div class="content margin-top-25">
            <h2>Domain rental examples</h2>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column">
          <figure class="image is-64x64 margin-bottom-25">
            <img src="/images/lib/material/resume.svg" alt="Resumes or Portfolios">
          </figure>
          <div class="content">
            <h3 class="is-bold has-text-centered">Resumes or Portfolios</h3>
            <p>
              Need to display your resume, portfolio, or personal website online?
              Rent a catchy, relevant domain name!
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column">
          <figure class="image is-64x64 margin-bottom-25">
            <img src="/images/lib/material/chart.svg" alt="Marketing Campaigns">
          </figure>
          <div class="content">
            <h3 class="is-bold has-text-centered">Marketing Campaigns</h3>
            <p>
              Use a catchy domain name to host your next marketing campaign.
              Renting ensures you only use the domain for as long as you need.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column">
          <figure class="image is-64x64 margin-bottom-25">
            <img src="/images/lib/material/mail-solid.svg" alt="eCards and Invitations">
          </figure>
          <div class="content">
            <h3 class="is-bold has-text-centered">eCards and Invitations</h3>
            <p>
              Don't just send a generic link that doesn't mean anything. Use
              a domain rental to convey that special message!
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="hero is-medium">
    <div class="hero-body">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="columns">
          <div class="column is-6 is-offset-3">
            <div class="content has-text-centered margin-bottom-75">
              <h1 class="title is-2 has-style-underline">
                Get early access.
              </h1>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
              <h3 class="margin-bottom-10 has-text-centered">
                Participate in the closed beta by signing up below.
              </h3>
              <form class="beta-form">
                <div class="control is-grouped">
                  <p class="control is-expanded">
                    <input tabindex="1" class="input is-expanded is-medium" type="email" name="betaemail" placeholder="Enter your email"/>
                  </p>
                  <p class="control">
                    <a tabindex="1" class="beta-submit button is-primary is-medium">Sign Up for Beta</a>
                  </p>
                </div>
              </form>
              <div class="beta-form-success is-hidden">
                <div class="notification has-text-centered is-primary">
                  <h3 class="is-white is-bold">Success! You have been put on the waiting list.</h3>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

    <%- include("../templates/footer"); %>
    <%- include("../templates/js_scripts"); %>
    <script src="/js/routes/main/main_beta_signup_logic.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
  </body>
</html>
